                    <msContents>
                        <!-- describe the intellectual content of an inscription -->
                        <summary>This grant records the donation of a village in order to maintain a shelter and feed the pilgrims in Kāci (Varanasi).</summary>
                        <!-- offers the possibility to give a summary of the inscription's content -->
                    </msContents>
                    <physDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <p>The plate has been ruled before being written. After the title, we find several images, from left to write: a trident, the sun, the goddess, a linga, a bull and the moon.<!--<foreign>ka</foreign> and <foreign>ta</foreign> are very similar.--></p>
                            
                        </handDesc>
